":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"公務員有冇番工都冇咩分別，home office 多一個月都得"},{"pid":"2895634148420bf0a28221f5c04fbd321db08948","tid":1876851,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"應該係聽雜總order夾硬逼鳩你地復工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed5e91cb443e5a152ddf4c7ed8719d43ef6e8b3","tid":1876851,"uid":60813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T22:07:13.000Z","msg":"復工就梗架啦，但係咪全面復工就未必，可能係一星期三日四日咁慢慢增加"},{"pid":"9b83aadc257625d25522aa5b00162907373a039a","tid":1876851,"uid":62148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T22:40:44.000Z","msg":"相信會<br />\n分分鐘隨時放到月尾"},{"pid":"c9dc75b5f9b1bbf09674e9d9cb9f7f4cfe7d43a4","tid":1876851,"uid":295637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d346eb6cadbfa92d434ac54f2f7bdf881bfca42","tid":1876851,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9dc75b5f9b1bbf09674e9d9cb9f7f4cfe7d43a4","tid":1876851,"uid":295637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"延咗啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/13/P2020021300287.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F13%2FP2020021300287.htm&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=a90f8b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/13/P2020021300287.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府延長特別上班安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  政府發言人今日（二月十三日）表示，因應疫情最新情況，政府會繼續實施部門的特別上班安排至二月二十三日，以減低社交接觸和病毒在社區傳播的風險。政府屆時會再檢視情況。<br />\n<br />\n  政府部門會繼續為市民提供緊急或必須的公共服務，以及提供基本和有限度的公共服務。如有需要，個別部門會就各項服務最新安排，另行作出公布。<br />\n<br />\n  政府發言人亦呼籲其他僱主彈性處理員工上班安排，盡量減少市民之間的接觸。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月13日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間11時10分"},{"pid":"d7351dc34c6967e4cc8df437e7ee6bde23444f28","tid":1876851,"uid":240250,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eed5e91cb443e5a152ddf4c7ed8719d43ef6e8b3","tid":1876851,"uid":60813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T22:07:13.000Z","msg":"復工就梗架啦，但係咪全面復工就未必，可能係一星期三日四日咁慢慢增加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"柒頭"}]}